      <url>/post/64a9b5c6.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="在maven的pom-xml配置文件中引入相应的jar包"><a href="#在maven的pom-xml配置文件中引入相应的jar包" class="headerlink" title="在maven的pom.xml配置文件中引入相应的jar包"></a>在maven的pom.xml配置文件中引入相应的jar包</h2><h2 id="在src目录下创建数据库的配置文件"><a href="#在src目录下创建数据库的配置文件" class="headerlink" title="在src目录下创建数据库的配置文件"></a>在src目录下创建数据库的配置文件</h2><h4 id="注意：我的mysql版本为8-0-，url那两行代码当时候调整一下，放在一行"><a href="#注意：我的mysql版本为8-0-，url那两行代码当时候调整一下，放在一行" class="headerlink" title="注意：我的mysql版本为8.0+，url那两行代码当时候调整一下，放在一行"></a>注意：我的mysql版本为8.0+，url那两行代码当时候调整一下，放在一行</h4><h4 id="其中-url的配置8-0-以上版本通吃："><a href="#其中-url的配置8-0-以上版本通吃：" class="headerlink" title="其中 url的配置8.0+以上版本通吃："></a>其中 url的配置8.0+以上版本通吃：</h4><h4 id="url-x3D-jdbc-mysql-x2F-x2F-localhost-3306-x2F-lby-db01-useSSL-x3D-false-amp-serverTimezone-x3D-GMT-amp-characterEncoding-x3D-utf-8-amp-autoReconnect-x3D-true"><a href="#url-x3D-jdbc-mysql-x2F-x2F-localhost-3306-x2F-lby-db01-useSSL-x3D-false-amp-serverTimezone-x3D-GMT-amp-characterEncoding-x3D-utf-8-amp-autoReconnect-x3D-true" class="headerlink" title="url&#x3D;jdbc:mysql:&#x2F;&#x2F;localhost:3306&#x2F;lby_db01?useSSL&#x3D;false&amp;serverTimezone&#x3D;GMT&amp;characterEncoding&#x3D;utf-8&amp;autoReconnect&#x3D;true"></a>url&#x3D;jdbc:mysql:&#x2F;&#x2F;localhost:3306&#x2F;lby_db01?useSSL&#x3D;false&amp;serverTimezone&#x3D;GMT&amp;characterEncoding&#x3D;utf-8&amp;autoReconnect&#x3D;true</h4><figure class="highlight properties"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#key=value</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">driverClassName</span>=<span class="string">com.mysql.cj.jdbc.Driver</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">url</span>=<span class="string">jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/lby_db01?useSSL=false&amp;serverTimezone=GMT&amp;characterEncoding=utf-8&amp;autoReconnect=true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#url=127.0.0.1:3306/db1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">username</span>=<span class="string">root</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">password</span>=<span class="string">123456</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#initial connection Size</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">initialSize</span>=<span class="string">10</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#min idle connection size</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">minIdle</span>=<span class="string">5</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#max active connection size</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">maxActive</span>=<span class="string">50</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#max wait time (5000 mil seconds)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">maxWait</span>=<span class="string">5000</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
